                <![CDATA[<p>平治近日在香港推出针对全线 EQ 系列电动车的全新 Mobile Service 流动售后服务，车主可在自行选择的地点安排维修服务，节省往返维修中心时间，提升日程便利性，体验真正的「Service at your convenience」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_133404-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_133404-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_133404-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲流动售后服务车</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240987" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121648-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121648-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121648-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240986" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121644-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121644-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121644-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1240990" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121904-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121904-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240606_121904-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style=